Package ch.ethz.rtc.kernel.util

Class Summary
Base64 Encodes and decodes to and from Base64 notation.
Base64.InputStream A Base64.InputStream will read data from another java.io.InputStream, given in the constructor, and encode/decode to/from Base64 notation on the fly.
Base64.OutputStream A Base64.OutputStream will write data to another java.io.OutputStream, given in the constructor, and encode/decode to/from Base64 notation on the fly.
DoubleMath SegmentMath provides methods to compare doubles.
Fraction Fraction represents a rational number as a fraction of a numerator and a denominator.
MathUtil MathUtil provides some mathematical methods.
Messages Messages provides a number of user interface messages.
Point Point represents a point in a cartesian coordinate system.
Vector Point represents a vector in a cartesian coordinate system.
